TopicTitle: the sufaceFX starts as soon as i load the ship/ kerbal cloning

Articles.Content:
when i load a ship on to the launch pad the ksp surface FX starts evan when my Rocket is not on and when i turn on the rocket no smoke would come out of the Rocket. on some rockets smoke comes out but never stops evan when i have no fuel left. when ever i try to eva a kerbal and put him back in his pod the pod tell me that its full and when i switch back to the pod there seems to be a kerbal already in the pod with the same name as the kerbal that is out side. im on ksp 1.02 32
